    "661060090411550992007/03/31 10:37:28BeviltorConfirmed,\
\
The Rocs will give you the eggs, and the Surf Gliders will drop the clams.  And Galgrom in the Caverns of Time sells the cheese.\
\
No need to leave Tanaris",
