    "2770188106101881062007/11/20 04:44:43gretchinrossI guess its worth mentioning.   I think this quest used to have a lower than 40 prereq, now it requires level 40, so don't be fooled thinking they (meaning blizz patch 2.3) screwed it up or something",
  },
