    "48661335020133502006/12/11 09:54:08ChandriallaYou *do* have to leave the instance to get the quest done. You would pretty much have to set up a group specifically for this quest. Have the mage make a portal to IF, then head to Burning Steppes and complete it. Otherwise, no one else is really going to want to hang around and wait while someone heads to Steppes unless everyone is there to do the quest. The little spiders also drop an item that clears the \"snare\" effect.",
