  ["WANTED: Caliph Scorpidsting46"] = {
    "278114638objectWanted Poster156561npcChief Engineer Bilgewhizzle74075050Gadgetzan350",
    "2781260111026012006/11/03 00:24:15QuigleyCaliph paths around near the water towers (http://www.wowhead.com/?npc=7847). Be careful, he's got 2 stealthed Wastewander Rogues following him around.",
    "2781120577101205772007/07/14 13:06:46RhasiAs a rogue, it's easy to time a Distract so that Caliph is pulled away from the two adds that patrol with him, and then take him out when they're a good distance away.",
    "2781205048202050482007/12/21 12:15:49Celice[small]\
(Note that this is an update of my post on Thottbot almost a year ago. I thought it would be useful here.)\
[/small]\
There are four water towers that form a [b]T[/b] shape: a central one at 61,34 and three around it to the SW, SE and NE at 60,37 63,37 and 63,31. Stand at the central one and you can see them all.\
\
[i]Caliph Scorpidsting[/i] spawns at the Waterspring camp at 58,39 near the SW tower, but don't try to kill him here as there are two [i]Wastewander Shadow Mages[/i] with their voidwalker minions waiting to interfere with you if you do. He is accompanied at all times by two stealthed [i]Wastewander Rogues[/i].\
\
After a minute or two [i]Scorpidsting[/i] walks off to the central tower at 62,35. From here he walks back most of the way to his camp. Then he returns to the central tower and goes on to the southern one at 63,37. If he gets this far without being killed his two bodyguards disappear completely and he breaks into a run back towards the camp where he started. On the way there he also vanishes until he respawns at the camp once more.\
\
So to find him, look first at the camp. If he's there then wait for him to move off and get him between the towers. If not then go via the central tower to the south tower. If you don't see him on the way then he's dead and you should go back to the camp to wait for him to respawn.\
\
This was easy with my rogue as I could use distract to freeze and kill each of the bodyguards in turn and then deal with [i]Scorpidsting[/i] himself.",
