    "27817117550711752007/04/22 17:23:32liquidiqHe is around 62,36 with 2 rouges.",
    "27818554710855472007/05/19 05:17:45sacredxavierif you're a melee class, you might wanna clear the mobs around the area before you try your luck with him; because if you're actually clearing the rogues first, they'll run away and you ain't gonna kill them in time if you get disarmed. \
\
otherwise, just kill caliph straightaway, and run - the rogues wouldnt stay on your tail for long. after that return and loot his head.",
    "2781210167111249982007/12/30 23:40:01Outlaw73Another warrior trick, or any class with a fear move is to go all out and kill Caliph first, loot his head, then fear the remaining guards and book outta there.",
