    "44816963231683482007/04/19 13:19:12MonsyYes, the person with the Arcanum can enchant it on someone else's item just like an Enchanter would.",
    "448119194711153312007/11/27 00:00:07spentlike he said for the shards dropping off all mobs, the highest drop rate(30%) is off of Jaedenar Hunters. and they can be found between  35,61  to  37,45 above ground and underground, the entrace to the cave that has them is at 35,58. hope this helps out",
