    "5211149569201495692007/09/05 20:30:56sorceressdee1- It is horribly difficult to run around finding these ghouls, so I advise you to go to the Auction House and buy 1 \"Elixir of detect undead\" http://www.wowhead.com/?item=9154 . This will allow you to see all near by undead on the mini map and hover over the dots to know what they are. This will save you a lot of time searching for them, since you can just go directly to them! The elixir is not expensive and it's well worth it. \
