    "5211200132202001322007/12/12 10:23:06Cross88The [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?npc=12337]Crimson Courier[/url] and her party can be a great asset to this quest. As they pass through Plaguewood and Corin's Crossing, they kill any undead in their path. Any ghouls they kill will still produce a Darrowshire ghost, and any other undead they kill may respawn as a ghoul.",
