    "51686505310650532007/04/10 14:16:30PoppaeaSoloed this as a lvl 59 Hunter. When you come to the right house. Dismiss pet. Run in and feign death in the far end of the room. Res and put out an icetrap. Call pet and heal up before you start to fight the Lord. Finally take on the two palas at the other end of the room. The book is now yours for the taking. The shield is outside the barn on the right corner from the front, not inside as has been suggested. It takes a little patience and is absolutely possible to solo.",
    "5168210115111853402007/12/30 21:40:57darth603Also the bulk of the mobs in Hearthglen are no longer elite as of 2.3, making this quest much more soloable. I actually had a harder time at Gahrron's Withering than I did fighting my way thru Hearthglen.\
