    "47431332801332006/09/12 23:19:27moslofHere is the short story...\
\
Go into the cave and find Emberstrife (http://www.wowhead.com/?npc=10321).  He is all alone so don't worry about ads.  Have the guy who is making the key, use the unforged seal in the water below the island (out of the aggro range of the dragon).  Ideally, the same guy who needs to forge the key will also aggro/pull/tank the dragon...with others healing and helping with DPS.\
\
Get the Dragon down between 20% and 10% health and then everyone stop attacking...the guy who is trying to forge the key needs to use the mind control orb on the dragon.  (Note: if your a hunter/warlock you should dismiss your pet before this fight...cause the dragon becomes a pet once mind controlled.)  \
\
Once mind controlled, then use the first spell on the pet bar (orange block with with a black dragon on it), and cast the spell such that you hit the seal on the floor.  If you mess up and he breaks MC...just recontrol the dragon with the mind control orb.   \
\
The rest of the party should wait for the all clear (key needs to be forged) before finishing the dragon off.  In the mean time just keep that guy healed.   You can and should mana up while the dragon is under Mind Control.\
\
Once forged, then you loot the seal on the ground.\
\
Hope this helps.  I did it with 4 people, two 60 Shamans, a 60Hunter, and a 55 Druid.  A shaman and the druid healed, the other Shaman tanked and forged, and the hunter just DPSed.\
\
Final note:  If you happen to be killed after you make him cast his forging spell but before you can loot the object, the forged seal object will remain long enough that you can run back from the grave yard and it will still be there.",
