    "39626120380612032007/04/02 16:52:42FaydenI found an easy way to get to Blazerunner by killing one or two elementals max.\
\
1) Go to 47, 52\
2) There's a cliff, you need to pass to its right. Try to jump, you may have a little trouble here, but it shouldn't take long.\
3) Go to 47, 49\
4) There's another cliff, but it's easy to climb.\
5) Finally, go to 48, 49\
6) Another cliff, also easy.\
\
You should be right next to Blazerunner. Though, you won't aggro him if you pay attention. I suggest you to run in the cave like mikedoh said.\
\
If you don't kill him fast, you may have to cast the spell to remove his aura. I figured it out after two deaths :p\
\
Good luck !",
