    "16911894980189492007/01/01 07:03:09WildWThe mobs you need to kill in this quest is found around 59.37 inn and around the smals tents. The rogues you need to kill are stealthed, so be carefull. The shadowmages can be a bit tricky also, because of their pets. Beeing 2 or 3 people when doing this quest is not a bad idea, since there are a clear risk of pulling many mobs...",
    "169113492121189492007/08/09 13:00:56darthvedaAll the mobs run when reduced to 15% health.  Keep them hamstrung/whatever you need to do to keep them from running to their buddies.",
    "16914447910444792007/03/01 09:23:16neelzfinchI managed to do this as a lvl 42 Mage. If you are lvl 42 or higher, you should be able to take all the mobs. There are both lvl 44 and 45 Assassins. Just watch out for aggro, as written above.",
    "169113819211325192007/08/15 06:27:40AevitasIf you're a hunter, here are some things to easily kill the mobs:\
\
Warlocks\
- Send your pet to attack the warlock.\
- Use multi shot to pull the voidwalker, then frost trap it.\
- DPS the warlock down then use intimidation and let your pet pick the voidwalker up.\
The warlock has shadow bolt for like 200 damage on your pet, so you might want to mend your pet every now and then.\
\
Rogues\
Use flares around the tents, to reveal the stealthed rogues.\
Place a hunters mark on their head after revealing them with flares, so they don't go back into stealth when the flare expires.\
\
Assassins\
Basically just let your pet tank, and dps the mob down, they do not have any special attack of some sort.",
