    "7603153077101530772007/09/14 19:28:09JaedxRaptureJust soloed this as a 53 affliction lock (http://www.wowhead.com/?talent=IVMriRfzVtbo0h ) with 240 shadow damage and 3.3k health (with imp out). Took a long time but wasn't at all *hard*. Here's what I did:\
