    "7603608012060802006/12/05 11:20:15MahmothSoloable at 60 or thereabouts.  The key to killing him is that he's Fearable, so you can mostly just wait 'till he's risen, Fear him, DoT him up, then send your pet after him.  He spawns in a nice, isolated bit of Felwood, so you almost certainly won't have any problems with adds from the craters.  Make sure you keep an eye on him in case Fear breaks early.  Keep a Health and SoulStone up, just in case, and if all else fails, banish'n'bandage.",
