    "7603148374201483742007/09/02 23:11:24VonaSolo'd as lv.51 Affliction Warlock with Imp (Had to re-spec. from my PvP favourite Dest.) Took around 7/8 attempts due to resists. Used 4 bandages and 2 healthstones in the end, Defiler's Talisman also came in handy when fear resisted.\
