    "64815960711164122007/09/27 21:01:28trev6917Tried this as a 46 Pally and died used this pic to clear the path somewhat beforehand the 3 47-48 scorpid spawn got me threw ran outta mana though and went down the repawns around were 2 fast and i had to kil along the way so bring mana pots and maybe have someone stay on route just incase",
    "648104000101040002007/06/14 00:23:44lordgregI soloed this quest as lvl46 hunter without any problem. Just stay behind a chicken a bit, when he aggroes, attack one mob after another with your pet, so your pet will take aggro for all three mobs attacking chicken. After that, just use mend pet on your pet, chicken will help you, throw few arcane shots on them and you're done.",
