    "584114162201141622007/07/02 00:55:10KittenBaneRemember that he spawns in front of the THRONE against the back wall of the temple's top floor.  He is on a very, very long respawn timer, so pray someone else hasn't been there before you.\
Went in as a Lv 37 War with a Lv 36 Mage.  You can get to him pretty easily if you hop on the wall's edge and just run past the mobs.  You won't aggro until you're near Nezz.  After we killed him, we hopped off the top floor's west side down to the ground, and then made our escape along the coastline via the temple's western exit.",
    "5846881121600892007/04/17 18:38:44Kriosnot true. you can climb up the side right to the first one and pull just him and another mob then walk along the side to the last.",
    "584166174101661742007/10/11 21:28:14darth603I soloed it on a 39 druid, but it was very trying. Basically, I stealthed up the back entrance, cleared a decent fighting area at the edge of the pool (literally, the rim of the pool, back a ways from the guy), and then single pulled the bulk of the adds. I rooted the add on Ganny's left, which somehow didn't cause the add on his right to aggro. Ganny came charging in, and became cat chow.\
\
