\
So yeah, it seems like Ganny and Nezzy are both linked to one add each, and pulling that add will get them without too much excessive aggro.",
    "5841973140197312007/01/07 18:48:16BeviselyntIn fact, they can be found at 23,7 and 23,9. Use the water pool to kill them, pull the mobs and swim there. Then, try to kill once at a time, trying to get out of battle with the others. It is not hard.",
    "584113990101139902007/07/01 18:03:34langbrRather than fight your way through what seems like a ton of trolls, you can skip to the top by going up the mountainous area on the East side of the troll ruins.  There you run along the wall until it meets the mountain.  Takes a few attempts sometimes but you can jump onto the wall in the corner where it meets the mountain. \
\
