Arlique, giddygamer.com",
    "584198783101987832007/12/09 22:18:04Gargler[url=http://www.wowhead.com/?npc=1061]Gan'zulah[/url] has a respawn timer of around 10-15 minutes in Patch 2.3.0. He's easily killed by a crowd control class and doesn't really do much damage to a level 41, as he's a 41 normal himself. He dropped [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?item=7472]Regal Boots of the Owl[/url] when I fought him.",
    "584150489201504892007/09/07 22:41:24GhosteAfter turning in the heads, interact with the cauldron to get these two quests:\
