    "70036903510690352007/04/18 08:12:05syntralThis was about as simple as they come I was onlt a level 46 when I did this quest and the mob's are level 47-49 very simple quest I recomment you do it at alone for the xp I was getting 100+ in a group and 300+ by myself",
