\
Anyway, the quest can be completed in either location I believe.",
    "8746202972202029722007/12/17 16:51:07Onochi181I soloed this with my mage at 44 and here's how: I went to Lost Rigger Cove and hugged the coast till I got to the fort. I walked in the main gate rather than going around to where the ships are, though. If you plan it just right you can pick off a lot of the lone walkers without drawing a crowd. You'll see Metzen right when you walk in but he's behind a few mobs. Pick off a few lingering pirates who might draw bigger mobs than you need. Then get ready, erect your mana shield, run towards Metzen, Blink then as the mobs swarm you quickly click on metzen to talk to him, (the sprinkle dust command is in the text box so don't worry about having your bags open), click to sprinkle the magical dust, he will be freed and you will be killed. It's sad but you can res at the healer for a quest complete and a job well done! Merry Christmas everyone!",
