    "4787122436201224362007/07/17 20:45:11CharlzOTo get to the egg, you must go through the cave to the end, through a bunch of 50s elites. The egg itself, is guarded by 3 mobs. You either need a group, or a good strategy to solo to get it.\
\
I was able to do it as a 50 Warrior. I had to die / spirit run the whole way through the cave, and then basically, pop Bloodrage while getting beat on enough to try an Intimidating Shout. The first time, two mobs resisted. The second, they all feared, giving me JUST enough time to loot the egg before dying..I spirit rezzed, and hearthed out to finish. Not an easy way, but possible.",
    "4787128414701284142007/07/28 21:27:43raddudedanSorry guys, this may seem not obvious to some people, like me. But the egg, to be clearer, is located in a cave. (As stated ^^) Heres how to get there. (Bring a fiend, suggested)\
\
1. Enter Jintha'Alor, you'll notice it's full of nasty troll elites.\
2. Work your way to the top of the \"temple\" (i suppose you can call it.) This isn't hard, just follow the roads and go up every set of stairs you come across.\
3. Keep gonig up until you see a the cave that is marked on your map. This is not the right cave, but it is close to it.\
4. Facing the cave, turn left. It is the very left route. You will enter a very opened - spaced, what you might call, ritual area. It is guarded by elite dogs, elite guards, and a named NPC. \
5. You will see also there is an altar in the middle of this place, with a horde troll on it, in a dead position. This marks the entry to the cave. The cave entrance is around where the troll is.\
6. Work your way through the cave. This may require some naked suicidal runs to save repair bills, and lots of corpse runs, which thankfully, are around the horde base, so it isn't too far. \
7. You'll come to the end of the cave, where there is another named NPC, and two guards patrolling in circles around the egg. It is very hard to kill these people to reach the egg, and can only be looted if they are not attacking you somehow. You cannot be bubbled, stealthed etc. I suggest bringing a friend with you so u can ninja loot it ^^\
8. Get the hell outta there, and pray you will never have to return. : )\
\
I hope this helps!!\
Good luck!",
