    "38016962150696212007/04/19 12:32:09marvin85860407To be more specific, he is in \"Forgewright's Tomb\" room and is on his very own tomb cant miss him. But u do have to be dead. If you plan on running the instace right after u get this quest the i suggest u dive off the ledge into the lava pit and run back dead from the GY, if not die close to the GY and then once u r done talking to him use auto-unstuck, ull b back in the GY with only feet to your body!",
    "3801134816601348162007/08/09 09:09:45moenbaseYyou can share it, but in order to complete it you have to talk to the man again. So it requires you to be in ghostform anyway.\
