\
Check some map for pyromancer loregrain if you cant find where to turn in this quest.",
    "380280214160802142007/05/09 05:53:07FishpawIt should be noted that the \"few rooms first\" mentioned in the excellent steps is actually in the area on the upper level surrounding Lord Incendras.\
\
You will go through the domicile and out into a half circle area with a short railing as the border.  If you go to this railing and look down, you'll see Lord Incendras pacing about.\
\
