    "4061176709201767092007/10/30 06:41:45SquirrelyThis quest was a complete pain in the ass for a lvl 53 mutilate rogue.  Drop rate is fine but the mobs in question are immune to gouge, poisons and blind and have huge armor.  Also, about half of the war reavers patrol around so you have about 50% chance of having another join in your fight at any given time.  Ended up dying about 10 times and taking 2hrs -_-.  Make sure you have your fights planned out well if you're melee.\
\
