    "7634163967701639672007/10/06 21:22:08RazielI just finished this quest today. It was quite a pain to figure out how to get this quest. Here's what you need to do:\
\
1.) Go to Molten Core and get the [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?item=18703]Ancient Petrified Leaf[/url] from [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?object=179703]Cache of the Firelord[/url].\
2.) Right click the leaf to start [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=7632]The Ancient Leaf[/url] quest.\
3.) Turn the quest in at [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?npc=14524]Vartrus the Ancient[/url] in Felwood.\
4.) Now speak with [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?npc=14526]Hastat the Ancient[/url] (he's right next to Vartrus the Ancient) and get the [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=7634]Ancient Sinew Wrapped Lamina[/url] quest.\
5.) Go to Azshara and kill [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?npc=6109]Azuregos[/url].\
6.) Loot [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?item=18704]Mature Blue Dragon Sinew[/url] from Azuregos.\
7.) Return to Hastat the Ancient with the Mature Blue Dragon Sinew to finish the quest. Upon completion you will recieve the [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?item=18714]Ancient Sinew Wrapped Lamina[/url] quiver.\
\
Notes: Obviously the hardest parts of this quest line are getting the Ancient Petrified Leaf and killing Azuregos.\
\
Good luck.",
