After you kill the Avatar of Hakkar[which you summon by using the egg] he drops \"Essence of Hakkar.\" Pick that up and right click it in your inventory to fill the egg with the Essence of Hakkar.",
    "3528100814010082006/09/25 11:44:45DracomageSet your looting to \"Free for All\" to have 1 person gather the Bloods needed for the encounter. Once Hakkar is summoned, change it back to Master-Looter.",
