    "6024677124183752007/04/15 15:25:04JaedxRaptureThis quest can be picked up from the rather large Torn Scroll in the tomb where Zaeldar resides. It's impossible to miss the scroll as it's gigantic and lighted slightly wrong, so it sticks out.",
