    "8306191612501916122007/11/26 12:38:50FantasyVLFew things you should know before doing this quest after patch 2.3.\
\
- She can be found in the deepest room of the cave, cave's entrance is at 54,88.\
-  She's level 62, non-elite, fights using priest's spells like Psychic Scream, Mind Flay and can stun with Blackout.  Due to the fact that she fears (a lot), clearing the room before the fight is recommended.\
-  She heals herself very often.  Her greater healing spell can heal her back to 100% hp with very little mana required, so if you intend to solo her, get ready for a very very long fight.  If you don't have any way to interrupt her healing, bring someone who can or better forget about this quest.\
