    "8306206341102063412007/12/24 02:12:43VetisWas playing on my 59 resto druid and figured I'd give this a roll as the last time I had ever been in silithus all the hives were elite and you couldnt rightly find a party for any of this stuff.   Now I've a pretty decent feral soloing set on this thing (stormshroud set, stuff from BRS, scholomance, strat, outlands) and I could not burn her down fast enough to maintain my mana from switching forms and healing, so quickly resorted to bear with the intent to outlast her, but she healed herself to full with as little as 50 mana and at one point when an extra mob joined in healed herself AND it to full while it nearly killed itself on my thorns.  fight lasted approx. 17 minutes (2 innervates, 1 mana pot, etc)before the room respawned and I died from overload of the mobs.  Even with clever usage of stuns when she was low hp and attempting to heal herself (war stomp and the bear stun) she would just stand there and keep trying until it landed.   So that being said I highly suggest bringing a friend or two, she'd be short work then.",
