    "268120317111962692007/12/18 02:16:19HibitaneI did run into a bug. After a servant of Razelikh went into 'spirit shock', and I wanted to use the stone, (I was standing very close to it) I got jumped by one of the felguard patrols, so I had to kill those first. \
