    "6148342214034222006/11/11 05:11:16sjunazDemetria herself is a shadow-priest type mob, with around 30,000 hit points.\
\
She is escorted by 8-10 adds, each of which can heal and be resurrected by Demetria -- if in range.\
\
The key to this encounter is to have a Mage bodypull the adds, and another member of the group use an instant spell on Demetria to separate her from the adds (which should be attacking the Mage). The adds have around 1200-1500 HP, so the Mage can easily kill them solo. However, the adds must ONLY be killed when they are out of range from resurrection by Demetria. \
\
Once the adds are dead, return to the group who should already be grinding Demetria's HP down. \
\
Grats on your new Bow/Wand/Shield!",
