    "76314106720410672007/02/23 11:34:45wisedrawesomeI've done that quest a lot of times now. I bought the mats, you need, if you want to be able to summon the steed and his master, and since that, other warlocks are asking me to summon the steed for them for a lower price ofcourse.\
