    "763110450131270462007/06/14 20:55:39unitepunxI helped a few 56/60ish guildies run through DM:W a few days ago, mostly for the lock in our group to get the Dreadsteed. At the end we invited in 5 more locks in rotation who all spoke to the pony and received their dreadsteeds. So it seems that in reality, the who thing is pretty worthless, since you can just basically wait it out.\
