    "89241903510190352007/01/02 00:07:29sportman1280It took 9 fuel for me.  The EP part of it is tricky because the ghosts are somewhat spread out.  I recommend you solo everything except the EP part.  This also helps save fuel as you find and kill ghosts a lot faster.\
