    "3518595620859562007/05/19 22:57:01SservisIf you want to solo these quests and need help, you can get Tooga to help if you haven't completed his quest (http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=1560).  Just be careful when the scorpians and bandits pop not to lose the chicken.  On the scorpians, the adds all went on Tooga and the chicken continued on its merry way.  I stayed to finish the adds and mounted to catch up, but I was a long way behind.",
    "3514674650467462007/03/05 19:38:25akmdwThe path that the robot takes is right through a group of 3 lvl 47 scorpids. Fortunately you can take them out beforehand. When you get near Steamwheedle port, a group of 3 wastewanders spawn, but they're all lvl 45.",
    "351113240101132402007/06/30 06:21:29caverDo you only get 1 shot at this? As when I died, I no longer had the quest item.",
