    "3516506321467462007/04/10 14:26:34bootsanatorDon't disregard the Wastewanders just because they're lower level. For me, one caster with a VW and two others spawned, and I killed the wrong two first. Yes, always kill casters first...escort quests are definitely not the time to forget that rule of thumb. The chicken died, then I died.\
Too bad, because those scorpids were Easy...yay for blade flurry, etc.",
    "35163937110639372007/04/08 15:18:20JohnJSalI'm going to post this message on all three of these \"Find\" quests, just in case someone doesn't see it on one of the other two.\
\
If you plan to do these quests in a group (which is very helpful, as any escort quest) everyone must first have completed the \"Find\" part of the quest, which means you have to find the chicken, choose \"Complete\" and then be *offered* the next part of the quest, which is the actual escort part. But do not accept this part until everyone has done the \"Find\" part, otherwise it won't be offered to them as escort quests normally are, because technically you are not on the same stage of the quest yet.\
\
So just complete the \"Find\" part, then when the next part is offered, decline it until everyone is ready to accept it.",
    "351203601102036012007/12/18 21:28:36BreakfirstHehe... I did this... Was not to hard... But then again, I cheated... Since I did it as a Hunter, and as allways that's ez-mode...\
