\
And a few bandages + Health pot never hurt any1... Good luck... Rest is as posted, reguarding position etc., and the reason the quest item is gone, is that the quest is completed, once you find the chicken.. The Escort-quest is the follow-up... Just abort, and go back to chicken start-position, if you die.. ;)",
