\
First wave was easy enough, needed food for the second, cleared the second, third came, quickly killed Mokk and we both mounted and ran.\
\
Simple instructions -\
Get quest from the Fin Fizracket (in the wrecked boat) at Booty Bay\
Run up untill you see the Elder Mistvale Gorrilas.\
Grind up to the cave collecting 10 Gorilla Fangs.\
Prepare yourself after speaking to Doctor Unbagwa.\
First wave (then use a bandage/potion)\
Second wave (then eat)\
Third wave (kill Mokk and then run)\
