    "7623126629301266292007/07/25 13:54:59supergroverI just finished this quest using my voidwalker (lvl 61) and I have zero talent points in demons.  It was very easy, not a prob or even a close death.  Didn't use pots, didn't use healthstone or soulstone either.  Anyway, thought I would put coords in for Ulathek, since I didn't see them here.\
