    "7623192498201924982007/11/27 23:25:58diskenthRemember that it's not the first cave when you reach Jaedenar, but the one past it! It will say \"Shadow Hold\" when you enter the correct cave! Just continue past the first cave and go through a winding path. You'll see a GREEN POOL at the correct spot, and the real cave near it.\
