    "7623200788102007882007/12/13 16:39:47DreadlordThe traitor is rediculously easy for a lvl 60 demonology warlock, i did use my voidwalker, but i did also hav improved voidwalker with all of his abilities at their maximum level, all u gotta do is stand on the small bone pile next to the traitor and then begin the event, send ur void in against him and Suffering should hit everyone, just DO NOT HIT SUFFERING, let him use it himself, he will use it wen they begin hitting u, this will ensure the suffering hits everyone.. then just curse of agony, corruption, immolation, death coil and 1 shadow bolt. Boom. he's dead.",
