    "38826228760622872007/04/05 00:34:38BeersterWith my level 52 Gnome Warrior I just collected them as I was doing this quest \"Shizzle's Flyer\" (http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=4503) By the time I got 6 Webbed Diemetradon Scales I had all 8 Dinosaur Bones. The drop rate is very similar to the Scales drop rate. Plust you can stay in areas with low level Deimetradon's that don't have level 53 to 57 elites walking around. :D",
