Aggroed 1 elit mob when i was doing the quest. I'm a lvl 52 warrior. Easy quest.",
    "3882173524101735242007/10/23 07:11:15RysenFor those of you who want to comlete this quest at lvl 49-50 (when quest is yellow), ignore above co-ords.\
