    "97253720050372002007/02/16 19:20:07LilyConfirmed, easy as heck for us paladins. Toss up Seal of Crusader, and use exorcism at max range to pull, backpedal for a second until Holy Wrath lights up, cast, Judgement, Consecrate, Seal of Righteousness, Crusader Strike if you have it, Stun Hammer, Judgement again when it's ready, and the engineer is pretty much dust. \
