    "608134670211068732007/08/09 00:34:50dctrjonsQuite frankly the quest lvl is incorrect.  Most often the quest lvl reflects the level of the highest MOB in the quest that must be killed.  In this case it is 3 lvls short.  If I'm not mistaken there is no quest lvl further off than this one.",
    "608200530102005302007/12/13 04:06:10sargetonyI solo'd this with my 44 NE Hunter. I didn't have any trouble at all. I would have my boar pull single mobs and then just kill them all from a distance. I actually cleaned out all three boats and both islands by myself. I only had to use one mana and one health potion once because Fleet Master Firallon has 2x guards and an Orc Warrior as bodyguards. I just set an explosive trap to keep the damage up and let my boar fight the FM and Orc while I meleed with the guards. I did have to keep hitting my pet with heal spells but other than that, this was pretty easy to solo as a LVL 44 Hunter.",
