    "7737203469102034692007/12/18 15:50:24XLiuhuJust got to 0/12000 Honored a minute ago. I just wanted to come here and tell you guys that it took me about 5 minutes and 42 seconds to spam the npc for returning these. Here's how to do it if you have all the 960 (as mentioned above) residues:\
