    "5721240417024042006/10/30 13:39:16osuracnaesI did this quest very easily with about 20 people - I'm sure you'd be fine with less.  The most important thing to do is keep Davil Lightfire and Captain Redpath alive.  Have the raid leader use the built-in symbols to mark them when they show up to make it a lot easier to keep track of where they are.",
