    "5721101152401011522007/06/09 04:31:32gnardaldid it with 5 players\
but a well organized trio can handle it too\
1) a tank that knows to hold aggro\
2) a mage that knows how to aoe\
3) a healer that knows to keep these two alive\
\
2-3 waves includes elite minibosses\
expect these waves a mage and a priest can handle easly until last wave where corrputed comes\
for these minibosses and last wave you need a tank that knows to keep aggro so that redpath is being kept alive.\
A funny quest that gives decent Agent Dawn rep. Some mobs give +1 a few gives +5 so all in all roughly 250~500 rep totally.\
\
P.S chest you need to open with the key given to you is behind Pamela.\
