    "652200958202009582007/12/14 01:46:50andyfThis quest is currently broken - the NPC is unlootable once killed. Will be fixed in an upcoming patch.\
\
http://forums.worldofwarcraft.com/thread.html?topicId=3407471939&postId=33489503170&sid=1#1",
    "6525323610532362007/03/18 15:26:38xiphiasManaged to do this mostly solo as a 41 warlock. Fear fozruk, kill his caster guard first, then his healer guard, then the melee guard. \
I did it with voidwalker, since I think that's the only pet that can take such a beating. \
After that it was some tricky fear-dotting of fozruk. It's tricky because he casts a stun if he gets too close, so if you don't hit the timing on fear 100% you get stunned and hit a couple of times.\
\
I only did it mostly solo, as two friendly alliance people started hitting fozruk in the back as he hit 1k hp :)\
\
Ysabell, Terenas EU",
