    "512538293118602006/11/18 02:38:12ZenimaAurius is at the chapel, just as you enter to the UD side from the backdoor.",
    "512516815110168152006/12/18 10:07:16kreghxThe Medallion of Faith is found in Human Strathholm about a third of the way into the actual 'scarlet crusade' part, inside of a small chest in a side room on the left of a hallway - this room contains a named mob that is for a quest (no loot, and I forget his name). \
\
