    "3063207376102073762007/12/26 03:47:42katsumadarknessHonestly, as a 47 Holy Priest this quest wasn't *horrible* but it was somewhat of a pain if you got bad pulls...the walk is a pain.  I did get all of my harpies fairly easily, though the Windcallers seem to have a large concentration in a small area where they're in a bowl-type place.  That is a *very* good place to stay away from unless you can kite them up over the ridge.  (which is very unlikely with the sheer number in there.).\
