    "293654144054142006/12/03 01:56:30OrmrissTheka the Martyr patrols a large room in the western part of Zul'Farrak.  The room is full of scarabs, but they are neutral beasts.  Just be sure to avoid using AOE attacks and they'll leave you alone.\
