    "5055176685101766852007/10/30 04:37:11A1winSoloed as 56 level fire mage (238 fire spell damage). Interrupt her Lightning Bolt and Venom Spit using Counterspell and Blink (to get out of range). Nuke whenever you are far enough. You'll probably need to use a healing potion and Mana Citrine, especially if you don't have as high spell damage as I had. Make sure you have a long clear way to run when kiting her.",
