    "60251569631801569632007/09/23 04:15:37TusvaInteresting bit there... she mentions the name Elling before stopping herself, most likely referring to [url=?npc=482]Elling Trias[/url], a Master of Cheese and, more importantly, sensitive information in the Alliance. Elling has contacts all throughout both continents, and it would appear he has Kirsta checking in on the Scarlet Crusade.",
    "60256342431583812007/04/07 17:06:36jaybaJust did this at 54 with my shaman.  Just ran up to the pallys outside the tower and dropped a stoneclaw totem to take aggro, then ran up the staircase halfway and dropped and earthbind totem. Reached the top looked around, completed the quest and jumped off.  Popped ghost wolf and  ran out in less than 2 min.",
