    "60255838130583812007/03/28 01:17:42NabopolasserI solo'd this as a 57 Frost Mage. \
\
It's the first tower you see when you enter the gates. You have to circle around to get to the entrance. When you enter the gates go to the left (the right leads to a lumberyard with lots of lvl55 non elites around it). A lvl61elite patrols the whole area so watch for him. \
\
My step by step: Ice Barrier, mount up, get to entrance, auto un-mount at tower, ice barrier again, use water elemental to draw one of the guards off, frost nova the other on the way up the stairs, circle the top untill it says complete, slow fall down to the top of the wall in front. I lost aggro after a few seconds, topped off health and mana, and slow fell down to the ground in front of the 2 guards at the gate. After a brief chase I was free. \
\
Total time: ~7minutes (had to wait for the 61elite to leave).",
    "6025117649101176492007/07/08 20:18:44Supernoradyou can mount up and run in to the top of the tower, jump off the tower and run out, the npc will still be on the top of the tower 5 sec quest =D",
    "6025141160301411602007/08/20 12:36:24ZombiePope[i]Normally[/i] the tower is free of mobs except for the 2 paladins guarding the front, but there's a [i]rare spawn[/i] called [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?npc=1841]Scarlet Executioner[/url] that sometimes shows up. He's a 60 elite.\
\
