    "36271495271201495272007/09/05 17:43:58kharzakhadThe NPC giving you an enchanted weapon to use against demons from this quest says something like: \"you can use it only once per three minutes\" - we evaluated it to be not true today. You can spam the weapon's use effect nearly continuously.\
\
Effects the weapon has on bosses (when used):\
[ul][li][b]Grol[/b] - it shrinks him, making his attacks WAY weaker. As a level 60 druid in bear form i had no chance to survive without using the weapon. Remember to use the weapon as soon as you see him grow back.[/li]\
[li][b]Lady Sevine[/b] - after few tries we discovered that using a weapon can interrupt her summoning of infernals. We were duoing it with a rogue as dps, and me - druid tanking, so only a rogue get to use her weapon and wasn't as effective as two people could be when it comes to interrupts, but it reduced the number of mobs hitting us.[/li]\
[li][b]Allistarj[/b] - we used a weapon on him of course, but I cannot say what it really did. We had no problems with downing him, and I believe each group (even group of two ;) ) doing this quest won't have problems here.[/li][/ul]\
\
