    "8947160npcAnthion Harmon16016npcAnthion Harmon160166600189261892718931189321893318934189351893718938189391894018941189432892928930389454894658947689487894988950",
    "89471467010146702006/12/13 06:14:06kreghxDrop this quest here and now. And save a lot of money. This crap only gets harder and harder, it is basically impossible to complete the whole heroism set in less than a month if you are not in a, say very helpful guild that's doing MC.(If you are, you shouldn't be doing this quest at all anyway). \
