    "89471560811146702006/12/14 18:17:19ShadaxWhile not wrong in his assessment of the cost of this quest chain, the goal of the 0.5 upgrade quest was missed.  Blizzard intentionally designed this chain to be somewhat difficult and expensive.  It's a means for non-raiders to get at least semi-decent epic gear.  All of the quests in this chain CAN be done with 5 (or 10 as appropriate) people who aren't all epic'ed out.  It's just not easy, or cheap.\
