However, considering the addition of the expansion in the very near future, I would have to agree.  Drop this chain, and put no more effort into it, unless you simply want to have one of each set of gear.  The gear you'll get from quest rewards in the expansion will EASILY be better gear than all of the rewards from this chain.",
