    "4501199298101992982007/12/10 19:38:35NorolasAs of patch 2.3, this quest awards 8,150 experience.",
    "450185832085832006/12/07 14:12:40RacaA pretty straightforward kill x, x number of times.  Watch out for aggro though, as there are all kinds of beasts bunched together where the pterrordax are.",
