    "5218155246211333542007/09/19 15:23:35SidonisThe point is you farm WPL mobs -fast- until you hit Honored, when they no longer give rep. You farm the skeletons in Andorhal or Felstone Field because there are -lots- of them to get Osseous Agitators from. -Then- you do all your WPL/EPL/Strat/Scholo quests and turn them in for rep. -Then- you sit there at the Felstone Field cauldron and cleanse it for as many osseous agitators / 6 that you picked up all this time. -Then- you go turn in all your scourgestones. This way you're not wasting rep.\
