    "9259207010111982662007/12/25 09:26:41MorbanthServer economy dependant, but on Defias Brotherhood, one stack of silk cloth costs 50s... so you're better off buying the silk from the auction house for 75 gold that you can get in 30 minutes by grinding primals or whatever. Don't waste your time grinding what you need, grind the best money you can and *buy* what you need.",
    "92591344440134442006/12/11 12:06:59GaoulThis is a quick, time efficient means of swapping your current bloodsail and booty bay reputation.   500 points per turn in, repeatable until you hit neutral with booty bay.\
