\
So assuming you only attacked Booty bay, and no other goblin city, you'll have neutral across the board with everyone by the time you hit neutral with Booty Bay.\
\
edit: quest description says 500//-455 rep.   I guess it was changed since I went through this :-)",
    "92591974451134442007/01/07 21:00:00AndurirThis is no longer accurate.  They recently changed it so that even after you reach 0/36000 hated with Booty Bay, you will continue to lose rep with the rest of the Cartel and by the time you are friendly with Bloodsail you will be at 0 with all four goblin towns.  This means you now have to do more work to get your reputation back to neutral with all towns.  See www.wowwiki.com/Bloodsail_Buccaneers for more information about rep with the Bloodsail and repairing Cartel rep afterwards.",
