  ["Chasing A-Me 0153"] = {
    "42455348npcA-Me 019623npcKarna Remtravel96186550424415348npcA-Me 019623npcA-Me 01962339501424324244424315348npcKarna Remtravel9618npcA-Me 01962326501424324244",
    "42451103370110332006/12/08 12:15:51mgarlandOnce you get passed the gorillas in front of the cave its a piece of cake. A-Me is fairly quick and the escort trip is short. Karna Remtravel is the NPC at the entrance to Marshal's Refuge from the tar pits. A-Me will take you there. I had no problems at all.",
