    "4245209395102093952007/12/29 14:45:44darth603A-Me has some interesting chat as well. I'll try to get a screenie of it, if I can do this quest without getting too much aggro. I had a lot of trouble the last time because of the monkeys calling each other- and new ones spawning.\
