\
While we are talking about references, the apes you fight for this mission drop empty barrels from time to time, like Donkey Kong.",
    "4243710362071032006/12/06 07:32:47omokusakiFirst, get a Mithril Casing from an engineer or from the Auction House.  They usualy go for around 2 - 5 gold.  You'll need this to finish the quest.\
\
Next, go to a level 49 dwarf female: Krana Remtravel in Un'Goro Crater, shes at 46.13. Take the quest from her.\
\
Then you are going to find A-Me 01 (a robot monkey). She is in the Fungal Rock (in Un'Goro crater), Cords to Fungal Rock are 63.17.\
\
Go inside the Fungal Rock and take the first turn to right, then you'll find her. She'll need the Mithril Casing to work.\
\
Use the Mithril Casing on A-Me 01 and she will start to work. Follow and defend her, she will take you back to Krana Remtravel at Marshal's Refuge.\
\
If you fail to defend A-Me 01 you don't need to buy a new Mithril Casing.",
