    "138021002711327502007/12/30 18:17:18KorruptiveI am a lv41 warrior and I solo'd it, best thing to do is have some potions and food ready, and a free slot in your bag, killing the first wave is easy, I am arms spec and I just used whirlwind and cleave for the first two enemies, with about 2/3 of my health left, used a potion to top it up, second wave did the same, and 3rd wave with the boss he walks up slowly so now is a VERY good time to use food you have whilst you are out of combat, hopefully you will have full HP after eating.\
\
