    "13808013720801372007/05/09 02:12:21EliseDid this quest with a 43 hunter with king B as pet. Used a combined strategy of the above. I let my pet charge in, laid down a trap, pulled one mob in the trap. My pet killed 1, and then died due to the massive damage Khan's cleave does!\
