\
BIGGEST TIP: Don't run through the graveyard in the central area at the bottom of the stairs of the temple. Infected Mossflayers will spawn everywhere. Make your way around one of the sides and jump over the wall at the bottom.\
\
At the base of the temple just to the right of the stairs the fourth tablet is resting against the bottom tier wall. A lvl 59 Shadowhunter is channeling next to it. He can be killed without aggro from other mobs.\
\
