    "6133134754111292612007/08/09 05:09:02dionfyrelytJust like to add to this that the protectors have about 4800hp, dual wield and have high armour....so meeting two at the same time is hard to manage solo, as you cannot kite at all in the densely packed lodge area",
    "613353803053802006/12/02 15:08:02magnarsYou can grab the registry from outside the building. Jump up on the ledge of the western wing, and search the wall left of the center with your mouse for the action-wheel. The elves are rather annoying, so this is the best way to solo this one. Good luck!",
    "6133129261201292612007/07/30 14:17:26CadsBook is guarded by two Quel'Lithien Protectors. They hit hard, they hit fast, they will attack from range, and they will interrupt your spells. In addition, the lodge and its surrounding area is packed very tightly with elves; inside the lodge there is a two-elf patrol that pats to the two protectors and the book.\
