    "8425173256301732562007/10/22 16:08:07tobarstepI wouldn't worry about what's replaceable and what isn't. Once you get to OL, [i]all[/i] of these are easily replaceable in about 2 hours.  Of all the class-specific level 50 quests, probably the only totally irreplaceable item is the Devilsaur tooth for hunters.",
