    "842514567113672006/10/04 14:08:10AthoriaI agree.  The trinket adds 75 str and 108 health regen over 1 min. Crusader adds 100 str, and heals for 75-125 instant, but only lasts 15 sec. I have not done the odds of the proc over time, but in my opinion, having a trinket that you can use when YOU want to use it, rather than something you have to wait and hope for, is much more valuable. \
