    "1126130589101305892007/08/01 16:41:24BoveyThe 1st post here is very misleading.  I died 3 times trying to take one down to < 5% health, then kill the other, etc.  This may be possible for a warrior, by as a 57 Rogue I don't have nearly enough armor to take that kind of beating.  It wasn't until I realized that YOU ONLY HAVE TO KILL ONE OF THE MOB'S and loot it that I was able to complete the quest.\
